# Hook: pre-commit-lint-fixer

**Event:** pre-commit
**Agent:** lint-fixer

Auto-fix lint and formatting issues before commit

When this hook's event (pre-commit) is triggered for files matching **/*.ts, **/*.tsx, **/*.js, **/*.jsx, activate the lint-fixer agent.
